						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the image of Vīrabhadra.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription is assigned to 7th-8th century A.D., on palaeographical grounds. Fragmentary. It refers to the son of Chōḷa-Mahārāju.</p>						

